solution.p:
Usando a Regra da Cadeia temos
\begin{array}{rcl} f'(x) \amp =\amp  \displaystyle  \frac{1}{2} (2 x^2 + 5 x + 3 )^{-1/2} \frac{d}{dx}
(2 x^2 + 5 x + 3 )
\\ \amp =\amp  \frac{1}{2} (2 x^2 + 5 x + 3 )^{-1/2} 
(4 x + 5 )
\end{array}
Substituindo x = 5 prodizimos:
f'(5)  = \frac{1}{2} (78)^{-1/2} (25) =\frac{12.5}{\sqrt{78}}

